<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">What is Full Face Waxing?</h2>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <p class="mb-4">
    Full face waxing is a process that consists of removing unwanted hair from your cheeks, <a href="/upper-lip-wax-phoenix" class="text-purple-700 hover:underline">lip</a>, sideburns, <a href="/eyebrow-waxing-phoenix" class="text-purple-700 hover:underline">eyebrows</a>, chin, forehead, and nose.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
